    "SCO": {
      "summary": "Scotland showed strong defensive organisation and competitive possession (45.2%) in 4-4-2, frustrating Morocco for much of match after conceding at 2 minutes. However, inability to register single shot on target from 6 attempts highlighted their attacking limitations in crucial Group C contest.",
