        "HENDRY and defensive unit kept Morocco to only 2 shots on target after early goal"
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "0 shots on target from 6 attempts — complete attacking bluntness throughout match",
        "Conceded in just 2nd minute, setting a difficult psychological tone for entire game",
